snippet.title: Hai-Shin 2 [Psx] - Intro
snippet.description:
Hai-Shin 2 is the sequel to the Playstation game Pro Logic Mahjong Hai Shin and is also mahjong game with different game modes:
- Special Play (free mode)
- Mahjong Grand Prix (story mode: Mahjong championship of 1998)
- Basic Study (Mahjong guide & dictionary)
- Mahjong Hands (practical tutorial)
- Tempai Mahjong (play tempai mahjong with his guide) 

Device:
Playstation Classic
Bleemsync 1.2
OTG
Sandisk Cruzer Blade 128 GB

Capture:
Ezcap 284 hd video capture
